source:
TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SEQ_00<tab>Maru seeks capable hands to help with a delivery.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>Règle spéciale<var 1D /var>:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
<var 1A 02 /var>Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe ou le job qui a servi à la commencer.<var 1A 01 /var>

Maru a besoin d'aide pour une livraison.
TEXT_BANARK125_04575_TODO_00<tab>Parler au ravitailleur au couvoir des hamsa

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_TODO_01<tab>Pick up the supplies for the Radiant Host quartermaster.
TEXT_BANARK125_04575_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the supplies to the Radiant Host quartermaster.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_TODO_02<tab>Livrer le matériel à la logisticienne

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_001<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, there you are. We've need of a stout pair of legs an' a strong back for a delivery, and you came springin' to mind...
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_001<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, tu veux bien m'aider pour une livraison<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_002<tab>The Radiant Host commissioned a major delivery, an' while the hippos hauled the supplies quick enough, we ain't got enough help off-loadin' them. You up for a bit of exercise?
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_002<tab>Les soldats de l'Ost rayonnant m'ont demandé de transporter du matériel. On a envoyé le plus lourd grâce aux hippopotames, mais il manque de la main-d'œuvre pour le déchargement sur place.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_003<tab>You'd be doin' us a huge favor, and make no mistake. If you're keen, talk to the Rider at the Hamsa Hatchery and he'll get you started straightaway.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_003<tab>C'est là que tu entres en scène. J'aimerais que tu ailles parler au ravitailleur près de la tente au couvoir des hamsa et que tu lui viennes en aide.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_010<tab>Ah, so you're the help that Maru sent word about, eh? Lucky you—we've just unloaded the carts, and all that's left is to bring them to their destination.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_010<tab>Oh, tu es là pour me donner un coup de main<var 1D /var>? Je viens juste de décharger les hippochars.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_011<tab>See that great tent over there? Take this crate over to the Radiant Host quartermaster waiting inside and the job'll be done. I'll be right behind you with the rest of the crates.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_011<tab>Il n'y a plus qu'à tout transporter jusqu'à la tente... Donne une caisse à la logisticienne de l'Ost rayonnant, je m'occuperai du reste.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>Deliver the crate of supplies to the Radiant Host quartermaster awaiting you at the specified location in the tent.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SYSTEM_000_012<tab>Apportez la caisse de matériel à la logisticienne de l'Ost rayonnant dans la tente avant la fin du temps imparti.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>You will have two minutes to complete the task. Should you fail, return to the starting location and begin anew.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_SYSTEM_000_013<tab>Vous pouvez porter cette charge pendant 120 secondes. Vous échouerez si vous n'arrivez pas à temps à destination, et devrez reprendre au point de départ.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_014<tab>Take one of the crates here and deliver it to the Radiant Host in the tent. I'll carry the rest.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_014<tab>Apporte une caisse à la logisticienne de l'Ost rayonnant qui se trouve dans la tente. Je m'occuperai de transporter le reste.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_030<tab>Ah, I take it those are the supplies we requisitioned! Apologies for the bulk─I can tell by the sweat on your brow that carrying them here was no easy feat.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_030<tab>Ah, voilà le matériel qu'on avait demandé<var 1D /var>! Ça n'a pas dû être facile de transporter une caisse aussi lourde, merci à toi.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_031<tab>It appears the other Rider will be along soon with the rest of the crates, so you can go ahead and thank Maru for another job well done.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_031<tab>Le ravitailleur va apporter le reste, tu peux retourner auprès de Maru.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_032<tab>The Rider should be here soon with the rest of the supplies, so let Maru know we appreciate him arranging all of this.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_032<tab>Le ravitailleur va apporter le reste, tu peux retourner auprès de Maru.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_035<tab>You've got what it takes to haul crates with the best of us, I reckon. I can handle the rest, so go and give Maru my regards.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_DELIVERER04575_000_035<tab>Merci d'avoir transporté le matériel<var 1D /var>! Ne t'inquiète pas pour le reste, tu peux aller voir Maru. Passe-lui le bonjour de ma part.

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_RADIANTSOLDIER04575_000_034<tab>What's that? Oh, I'm just waiting for the supplies we've ordered. They should be here any moment now...
TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_040<tab>I'm guessin' the supplies made it without a hitch? Another job well done─but I ain't never doubted you.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_040<tab>Tu as aidé au transport du matériel<var 1D /var>? Merci<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_041<tab>Havin' folks like the Radiant Host as our regular partners gives our business some legitimacy in Radz<var 1F /var>at<var 1F /var>Han, but we'd never have made it this far in buildin' relationships without your help. Your contribution's been noted─wrote it down an' everythin'.
target: TEXT_BANARK125_04575_MARU_000_041<tab>Qui aurait cru qu'une or<var 16 /var>ga<var 16 /var>ni<var 16 /var>sa<var 16 /var>tion publique comme celle des soldats de l'Ost rayonnant commercerait avec nous... Je suis sûr que ton soutien y est pour beaucoup. Espérons que tu nous lâcheras pas de sitôt<var 1D /var>!
